#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"WebinarIgnition is a premium webinar solution that allows you to create, run "
"and manage webinars. Build and fully customize, professional webinar "
"registration, confirmation, live webinar and replay pages with ease."
msgstr ""
"WebinarIgnition adalah solusi webinar premium yang memungkinkan Anda membuat,"
" menjalankan, dan mengelola webinar. Buat dan sesuaikan sepenuhnya, "
"pendaftaran webinar profesional, konfirmasi, webinar langsung, dan halaman "
"pemutaran ulang dengan mudah."

#: UI/dash.php:13
msgid ""
"WebinarIgnition offers a variety of pre-built webinar room designs that are "
"modern, professional, and engaging. These designs are easy to customize with "
"your own branding, and they can be used for a variety of different types of "
"webinars, including lead generation webinars, customer education webinars, "
"and product demos."
msgstr ""
"WebinarIgnition menawarkan berbagai desain ruang webinar siap pakai yang "
"modern, profesional, dan menarik. Desain-desain ini mudah disesuaikan dengan "
"merek Anda sendiri, dan dapat digunakan untuk berbagai jenis webinar yang "
"berbeda, termasuk webinar perolehan prospek, webinar edukasi pelanggan, dan "
"demo produk."

